OL,3,CJoey Barton charged with alleged
OL,4,Cassault near golf club
OL,6,FJoey Barton has been charged with an
OL,7,Falleged assault.
OL,9,FThe former Manchester City footballer
OL,10,Fand podcaster was one of two men taken
OL,11,Finto custody by Merseyside Police
OL,12,Fafter emergency services were called
OL,13,Fto Fairway, near Huyton and Prescot
OL,14,FGolf Club, on Sunday at 9pm.
OL,16,FMerseyside Police officers found a man
OL,17,Fwith injuries to his face and ribs,
OL,18,Fwho was taken to the hospital for
OL,19,Ffurther treatment. The force says he
OL,20,Fis in a serious but stable condition.
