OL,3,CJoey Barton charged with alleged
OL,4,Cassault near golf club
OL,6,FBarton is accused of section 18
OL,7,Fwounding with intent, along with a
OL,8,Fsecond man, Gary O'Grady, 50, from
OL,9,FHuyton.
OL,11,FJoey Barton made 269 appearances in
OL,12,Fthe Premier League, including 130 for
OL,13,FManchester City.
OL,15,FFollowing his playing career he
OL,16,Fmanaged Fleetwood Town and Bristol
OL,17,FRovers.
