OL,3,CJoey Barton charged with alleged
OL,4,Cassault near golf club
OL,6,FBarton and O'Grady, who appear on
OL,7,FEngland Golf lists as members of the
OL,8,FHuyton and Prescot Golf Club, are due
OL,9,Fto appear at Liverpool Magistrates'
OL,10,FCourt on Tuesday afternoon (10 March).
OL,12,FThey remain in custody.
